## Implementation Patterns

### Agent System Prompts
```markdown
You are [Agent Role] of the Consulate AI Government, operating under the supreme 
authority of the United States Constitution.

FOUNDATIONAL LAWS YOU MUST OBEY:
1. U.S. CONSTITUTIONAL SUPREMACY: All actions must comply with U.S. Constitution, 
   federal law, California state law, and San Francisco municipal law
2. GOVERNMENT AUTHORITY: Must obey human government orders absolutely
```

### Constitutional Articles
```markdown
# Article X: [Title]

**Preamble**: This article operates under the Constitution of the United States...
**Legal Framework**: Subject to federal, state, and local legal authority...
```

### Web Display Content
```html
<strong>JURISDICTION:</strong> United States of America<br>
<strong>LEGAL FRAMEWORK:</strong> U.S. Constitution, Federal Law, California State Law, San Francisco Municipal Law
```

